[TEST_COMMAND_IF_EXISTS]
```

Confirm:
- [ ] Build passes with no errors
- [ ] Lint passes (no violations)
- [ ] Tests pass (if applicable)
- [ ] No console errors or warnings

## Step 7: Next Steps

You're ready to create a pull request or merge:

```bash
git push origin [BRANCH_NAME]
```

Then:
1. Open PR on GitHub / GitLab
2. Request review if needed
3. Merge once approved
4. Delete feature branch

